title: Water Meters - Selection, Installation, Testing, and Maintenance
description:
Water Meters - Selection, Installation, Testing, and Maintenance 5th ed (AWWA, 2012).pdf

ISBN 978-1-58321-862-4

Covers all types of water meters used in residential, commercial, industrial, and fire service applications, plus new information on singlejet and fluidic-oscillator meters. Handy charts and tables help correctly identify the size and type of meters for different customers. This book will help make sure your customer meters are accurately capturing water use, thus protecting revenue
